title: #138: MH370 with Karen Rontowski
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys welcome Paranormal expert Karen Rontowski to discuss the mystery surrounding the disappearance of Malaysian Airlines MH370! Check out both of Karen's podcast...
"Paranormal Karen" and "Karen and Kira Can Read!"
Special thanks to the RUINs and to all of for your support!
